    "instruction": "From metric.csv, compute global statistics for each (cmdb_id, kpi_name) time series using the full available data (do NOT filter by incident window when computing these statistics). For each series compute: count, mean, min, P5, P95, max. Then for the incident window March 21, 2022 22:30:00 to 22:59:59 (UTC+8) report: number of points in-window and earliest in-window timestamp (or null if none). Restrict the output to the top 30 (cmdb_id,kpi_name) series ranked by (P95 - P5) descending. For each returned row include: cmdb_id, kpi_name, count, mean, min, P5, P95, max, points_in_window, earliest_in_window_timestamp. Return results as a JSON-serializable table (limit rows to 30)."
